                        <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">FACT #1</h3>
                        <p class="feature-box__text">
                                Childhood trauma is very common, even in employed white middle-class, college-educated people with great health insurance. There is a direct link between ACEs and adult onset of chronic disease, such as depression, and suicide. An ACE score of just 1 makes us twice as likely to become an alcoholic.
                        </p>
                    </div>
