                        <p class="feature-box__text">
                                More types of trauma increased the risk of health, social and emotional problems. People usually experience more than one type of trauma – rarely is it only sex abuse or only verbal abuse. A whopping two thirds of the 17,000 people in the ACE Study had an ACE score of at least one — 87% of those had more than one.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
